    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable ride that's ready for its next chapter? This vehicle is in fair condition and offers a solid, reliable driving experience for anyone seeking great value. While it shows some honest wear and tear from its years of service, it remains a sturdy companion that\u2019s perfect for daily commutes or as a practical second car!",
