      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle has been maintained to the most exacting standards, preserved in showroom condition both mechanically and aesthetically. With an impeccable service history and a flawless exterior finish, it represents the pinnacle of its class. An acquisition for the sophisticated driver who demands nothing short of excellence.",
      "price": 48500.0,
